01:02:16.820 --> 01:02:19.820
the Suriname branch oversees translation

01:02:19.820 --> 01:02:22.820
into five other languages.

01:02:22.820 --> 01:02:25.820
Surin and Tango, Aachen,

01:02:25.820 --> 01:02:29.820
Saramakan, Suriname Sign Language, and Karab.

01:02:29.820 --> 01:02:34.820
In 2022, 20 translators in Suriname Bethel

01:02:34.820 --> 01:02:37.820
